snippet.title: Game & Watch - Turtle Bridge (c)1982 Nintendo [MAME emulation footage]
snippet.description: This is Nintendo's Turtle Bridge, from the Game & Watch series, running in MAME.  Emulation by algestam.  The background artwork was provided by hydef and can be found at https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1IbSRYTfKoKDgZfJZTZdnKFSpBvCvgJZV
